{
  "texts": [
    "First, we review the maintenance approaches and the role played by PHM.",
    "We then explain what non-technical and technical text data are, and how text from MWOs is unique.",
    "We demonstrate how traditional NLP fails on technical text, the why there is a need for TLP.",
    "We propose a TLP framework to implement in the PHM environment and suggest some potential areas of its use.",
    "To demonstrate the capabilities of the proposed framework, we identify two scenarios using MWOs of aircraft and apply customized text processing methods to it."
  ]
}